RNotes | EBImage

library(EBImage)

thresh

x <- readImage(system.file('images', 'nuclei.tif', package='EBImage'))
display(x, all=TRUE)

y <- thresh(x, 10, 10, 0.05)
display(y, all=TRUE)

y <- thresh(x, 30, 30, 0.15)
display(y, all=TRUE)

y <- x > otsu(x, levels=4)
